text: Lord Holland may refer any of the holders of the following titles: * Earl of Holland, created in the Peerage of England in 1624, became extinct in 1759 * Baron Holland ** Baron Holland of Holland in the County of Lincoln, created in the Peerage of England in 1762, became extinct in 1859 ** Baron Holland of Foxley in the County of Wiltshire, created in the Peerage of England in 1763, became extinct in 1859
title: Lord Holland
